      "tree": {
        "sha": "d68adfe24ab9b05d4672f24d896d1f0e2218d7ee",
        "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin-core/gui/git/trees/d68adfe24ab9b05d4672f24d896d1f0e2218d7ee"
      },
      "verification": {
        "verified": true,
        "reason": "valid",
        "payload": "tree d68adfe24ab9b05d4672f24d896d1f0e2218d7ee\nparent 18c05d93016b28a9afd4c716dfe00b6e0accb30b\nauthor Hennadii Stepanov <32963518+hebasto@users.noreply.github.com> 1784478182 +0100\ncommitter Hennadii Stepanov <32963518+hebasto@users.noreply.github.com> 1784478182 +0100\n\nqt: Fix `-Wsfinae-incomplete` warnings when building with GCC 16.x\n\nAccording to the CMake documentation for `AUTOMOC`, all `moc` output\nfiles that are not included in a source file are aggregated into the\nCMake-generated `<AUTOGEN_BUILD_DIR>/mocs_compilation.cpp`, which is\nadded to the target's sources.\n\nWithin that single translation unit, `moc`-generated code checks the\ncompleteness of a signal or slot parameter type while it is still only\nforward-declared, and the type is completed later, when a subsequently\nincluded `moc_*.cpp` file pulls in the header that defines it. GCC 16.x\ndiagnoses this pattern with the `-Wsfinae-incomplete` warning, which is\nenabled by default.\n\nIncluding the `moc` output files at the end of the corresponding source\nfiles excludes them from `mocs_compilation.cpp`, so each one is\ncompiled in a translation unit where the relevant types are complete.\n",
        "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niQIzBAABCgAdFiEE0dvyxLlvLev0wWZUQQEIES5+qB8FAmpc+eYACgkQQQEIES5+\nqB9tEg/+OAsBDPh9AbFB0O5CDP2gU+644pFoIdQNaKTv9DBFNjtO+E5kfWRJ7jci\nnb/z/kHdP3kl3vwle5KfXqCWMtgU0Ig5xMSV5adxe4C8c4gLvVWsS/Yjlz+lHUGv\nzB1QP/KLe8uVS4upflqRtHLgAq+50jN+npckZvzJTLLWyyfpaW/7OSTG9PwlAtR+\n5DFSYTdo74U2M6sLdFSKqlBlogs1jbZLacm6eQF9rMCxbU4zs3OAaMpMVI/lsZZU\n7cPbkxXPFQvUMr5Hh+de4SwT6/oLeQQhWaG7rdOMXhgRCxVIh6oGnpKSQRrwPnnZ\nsj2lYDu0lD1q5PZGpDrRHkfpeiHkgtyg7AR3xEYI6BXXfO44Tf4jfukOH5l3DsJz\nA67obcNB9Of81pp1K0wQy1RZlrjYwXfa7aRQ3hQYULJ7E9mZmQGjZba1bFNKavV1\nEbZ++wyGF4UgQjJB6En5rc7oOSHHyUfVVYgOwMVcmsLHZ+6O7/iiHLuisKbeb46v\nsvl8oJG+ph3scHfT7NIv6P8QJ5H2c3z5LffL2Rud1u4ZzbtWhCpBXJ5zKAvu91R2\n6J9ljbuU/1dUHNWkLn1yb9mWT5Q2ca31tF42IjrPN7ga8725lCriJIZqp+bmyonq\ndwjMV+RzVTDKDtSgsfw1MJxYGf3MNVDQPmo599DZYylcuyhDKoU=\n=rU71\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----"
